lead_paragraph: Chad le Clos's much-anticipated re-match with superstar Michael Phelps in Rio de Janeiro's Olympic pool is clouded by a family health scare that hangs heavily over the 24-year-old South African.

headline.main: Cancer Scare Weighs on Le Clos Ahead of Phelps Re-Match
